{"id":"a70c9fe4-f471-48b3-9a6b-b0b30dba56e3","name":"You are NOT HIM, You will NEVER be HIM, you are NOTHING","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nUxlqgWmZxXVtywU2LQXZ.gif\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>YOU WERE DEFEATED</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>He did his best to prepare you for the Final Duel, but you just aren't good enough.</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/J5Kl6VuSzqXCPIYyb9eZr.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>You weren't strong enough.</strong></span>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/R9o9B5hw1kkq1x-kIGHHc.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Knightess defeats you handily</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/22okRBIde-cYoubvACpl9.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>And you are exiled, dishonored, and most importantly, the city is left defenseless to her authority</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>YOU ARE NOT HIM</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdo